import { createApp } from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import router from './router'
import './assets/css/tailwind.css'

// 引入Font Awesome
import { library } from '@fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core'
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/vue-fontawesome'
import { faTshirt, faSocks, faUserTie, faSun, faShoePrints, faGift, faHeart, faHeartO, faPlus, faSearch, faBellO, faUserO, faCog, faSignOut, faMagic, faArrowRight, faChevronLeft, faChevronRight, faCloudUpload, faCloud, faLightbulbO, faBarChart } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'

// 添加需要的图标到库中
library.add(
  faTshirt, faSocks, faUserTie, faSun, faShoePrints, faGift, 
  faHeart, faHeartO, faPlus, faSearch, faBellO, faUserO, 
  faCog, faSignOut, faMagic, faArrowRight, faChevronLeft, 
  faChevronRight, faCloudUpload, faCloud, faLightbulbO, faBarChart
)

createApp(App)
  .use(router)
  .component('font-awesome-icon', FontAwesomeIcon)
  .mount('#app')
